text: Kaiserstuhl was a municipality of the district of Zurzach in the canton of Aargau in Switzerland. On 1 January 2022, the former municipalities of Bad Zurzach, Baldingen, Böbikon, Kaiserstuhl, Rekingen, Rietheim, Rümikon and Wislikofen merged to form the new municipality of Zurzach. == References == ==Other websites== Category:Former municipalities of Aargau Category:Cities in Switzerland
